      "acceptanceCriteria": "Richardson extrapolation-based GCI must be computed on at least three systematically refined meshes for the hemolysis QoI.",
      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study performed; GCI for normalised hemolysis index is 4.1 % on the finest mesh. Mesh study was conducted under the released build. Achieved level 3 vs required level 4."
