      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Predicted hemolysis index must be compared quantitatively against experimental measurements with uncertainty bounds on both simulation and experiment; comparison metric must account for experimental scatter.",
      "rationale": "Quantitative comparison performed for all five operating points under ValidationResult vad-hemolysis-vr-01. Normalised hemolysis index error ranges from 3.2 % to 7.8 %. However, this ValidationResult was generated under ModelConfiguration ansys-cfx-15-build-2026-q1-build-7-rc2, whereas the model of record is ansys-cfx-15-build-2026-q1-build-7. The responsible engineer assessed the two builds as effectively identical based on the change log, and no re-run was performed under the released build. Experimental uncertainty bounds are partially characterised. Achieved level 3 vs required level 5."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
