      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation domain (geometry, fluid, operating range) must closely match the COU domain for the VAD device.",
      "rationale": "Validation performed on FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry; COU device is a proprietary VAD with similar but not identical impeller geometry. Fluid properties (bovine blood surrogate vs human blood) introduce additional extrapolation. Achieved level 2 vs required level 4."
    },
